Urge urinary incontinence can be a disorder caused by destroyed pelvic structures.

 We repaired the uteri-sacral ligaments (USL) by cesa or vasa.

 The study evaluates if solifenacin can lead to continence after surgery or if also the pubo-urethral ligaments (PUL) need to be repaired.

